{"tid":1789728,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"中小學學英文嘅通病","createTime":"2019-12-19T13:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T08:59:19.000Z","uid":64694,"like":119,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"12fa1ad863694add79d2c8f076f46785249fcc6c","tid":1789728,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:14:36.000Z","msg":"由細到大都叫人死記硬背，背字典背vocabs，但係問題係如果係唔係英中而係中中嘅話，生活上應用英文唔夠多，可以話少之有少，試諗吓你平時幾時會講英文？返屋企用廣東話，返學溝通用廣東話，實際上每日得1-2堂講英文學英文，平常應用不足，而且平時考完試，好多時考完就咩都唔理咩都唔記得晒，將之前學嘅嘢拋諸腦後，之後又重新再學過，完全冇咗階段性學習，所以搞到有啲人連一句英文嘅完整句都講唔到<br />\n<br />\n原本有適當嘅input應該要有返適當嘅output先可以平衡返<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uH5PdDO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuH5PdDO.png&h=fe9a9958&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係而家得大量input冇output，結果導致好多input同take in咗嘅嘢（即係之前背落嘅大量vocabs）都忘記晒，到最後就付諸流水喇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hVNxVUK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhVNxVUK.png&h=5b433ea0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n感覺上就好似多啦A夢入面大雄屙走晒啲記憶麵包咁，所有吸收咗嘅嘢最後都一次過流失晒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/crrKM2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcrrKM2f.jpg&h=3fb59b5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Huh2yHf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHuh2yHf.jpg&h=a74fdcd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EExRr2g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEExRr2g.jpg&h=1ac78840&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GWvr0ng.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGWvr0ng.jpg&h=4e76664a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/98DdFnh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F98DdFnh.jpg&h=da27ce84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得董伯伯喺教育制度上有好有唔好，唔好就係佢推行母語教育，搞到大家英文差晒，但係好嘅係佢推行咗通識教育，等大家有咗獨立思考，唔使俾人洗咗腦都唔知<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dcSepQd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdcSepQd.jpg&h=de51ce10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁點樣可以改善呢？<br />\n除咗從生活上著手用多啲之外，重可以睇多啲片同聽多啲listening，因為影音作品入面嘅畫面同聲音比起純文字對個腦有更大衝擊性，有好強勁嘅刻劃，見到聽到之後幾乎可以即時勾起深刻印象同回憶，就好似話你一見到下面兩幅圖就會即時諗起<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PKt9dLR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPKt9dLR.jpg&h=ab333efd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T9U4M5R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT9U4M5R.jpg&h=cf7fff2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天線得得B<br />\n<br />\n另外，其實任何嘢都有兩面，雖然成日話洗腦唔好，但其實佢都有佢嘅好處<br />\n<br />\n好似話學英文可以不斷重覆聽listening，不斷洗自己腦，上面提到人類對聲音比文字更敏感，對個腦有更大impact，好似話你成日聽let it go let it go，聽聽吓自己都識得唱咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ytpkkr8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fytpkkr8.jpg&h=9d0f225b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重有如果聽listening有時速度一開頭太快，可以將listening開0.5倍速聽，聽清楚個句子結構，合埋對眼，喺一片黑暗之中，可以順便訓練想像力，想像返佢個畫面出嚟，諗返個環境係點，喺黑暗之中繪畫返出嚟"},{"pid":"d9a4759b38ee7fc5dea435542f76ff764abe0743","tid":1789728,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:14:58.000Z","msg":"Twitter戰線:要令星火事件上到國際！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789690</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">幫手入去將星火推到上國際</span>"},{"pid":"864323c7774167277126e6251014dd12ba834779","tid":1789728,"uid":88940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:15:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://t.me/xmasevehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fxmasevehk&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfInMh2OwnA7FCi%2BsKpr4SDY%3D&h=cfc1f596\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/xmasevehk</a><br />\n唔好意思借一借位<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">經濟攬炒！香港人果七千萬比人搞啊！佢老母仲OT成九億<br />\n1221<br />\n1224<br />\n1225<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji